Detailed Description

cvmx_zip_cmd_bist_result

ZIP_CMD_BIST_RESULT = ZIP Command BIST Result Register

Description: This register is a reformatted register with same fields as O63 2.x. The purpose of this register is for software backward compatibility. Some bits are the bist result of combined status of memories (per bit, 0=pass and 1=fail).
